# ============================================================
# ~/.claude/ sync, exclude secrets, machine-specific state,
# caches, logs, and conversation history. Track config, skills,
# plugin blocklist, and memory.
# ============================================================

# --- Secrets (NEVER commit) ---
.credentials.json
config.json
*.pem
*.key

# --- Machine-specific overrides ---
# Claude Code merges settings.local.json on top of settings.json at load
# time. Use it for OS-specific permissions, local env vars, dev endpoints.
settings.local.json

# --- Stale settings backups ---
settings.json.bak
settings.json.orig
settings.json.pre-*
*.backup.*/
backups/

# --- Logs & telemetry ---
*.log
bash-commands.log
cost-tracker.log
history.jsonl
stats-cache.json
telemetry/
usage-data/
metrics/
homunculus/

# --- Caches & transient state ---
cache/
downloads/
paste-cache/
file-history/
ide/
session-data/
session-env/
sessions/
shell-snapshots/
tasks/
.buddy-reroll.json
.last-cleanup
project-config.json
security_warnings_state_*.json
mcp-needs-auth-cache.json

# --- Daemon & background jobs ---
# Supervisor process state (PID, status, worker roster, named pipes) and
# per-job working directories. Rewritten every time the daemon starts.
daemon.lock
daemon.status.json
daemon/
jobs/

# --- Plugins: ignore entirely ---
# All of plugins/ is runtime state, caches, marketplace clones, and
# per-machine manifests that get rewritten on load. Plugin enablement
# lives in settings.json → enabledPlugins (currently empty).
plugins/

# --- Projects: ignore entirely ---
# Conversation history, todos, shell-snapshots, and auto-memory are all
# per-machine/per-session state. Not worth syncing, each machine's
# Claude Code maintains its own projects/ content.
projects/

# --- Editor / OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# --- Per-machine skill data ---
# Each skill that needs machine-specific config keeps it in its own folder.
# The .example.md template is committed; the real file is per-machine.
skills/deploy/HOSTS.md
skills/frontend-design/PREFERENCES.md
skills/note/VAULT.md
skills/query/VAULT.md
